    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Bring a medium pot of salted water to the boil, then reduce to a simmer. Add the soba noodles into the pot, rest the sieve or steamer basket with the kale on top, then cover with a lid. Cook the noodles following packet instructions, then drain and place the noodles and the cavolo nero into a bowl."
    },
    {
